  "texts": [
    "Despite this potential danger, we believe that the present manuscript provides a reference point from which it will be easier to develop definitions applicable to search situations in which some of the definitions laid out here are not useful. 2.",
    "It is important to keep in mind that some of the definitions provided here are tied to the current state of knowledge in our field.",
    "As new data accumulate, some of these might have to be updated, and new terms might have to be introduced.",
    "The main thrust of our endeavor, however, is that unnecessary proliferation of terms, as well as ambiguity and imprecision with regard to their definition seriously hamper scientific progress.",
    "We hope that promoting a more rigorous attitude towards terminology will discourage authors from obfuscating theoretical concepts by employing unspecific or misleading terms to immunize their own theory against criticism."
